# Build context now spans the repo root so the Dockerfile can COPY
# mise.toml/mise.lock. Exclude everything that isn't needed in the
# image build to keep the context small.
#
# Note: builds/podman-rootful/ and builds/podman-socket/ are re-included
# (negated) because those Dockerfiles also use the repo root as their
# build context and need to COPY their per-build config (requirements.txt,
# containers-storage.conf, containers.conf).
.git
.github
.claude
.cursor
.gitignore
adr/
bin/
builds/
!builds/podman-rootful/
!builds/podman-socket/
devcontainer_setups/
doc/
docs/
dotfiles/
envs/
tests/
README.md
CLAUDE.md
Makefile
renovate.json
renovate-base.json
